{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You are alone, whether you're out there with your best friend, or your father, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Once you reach a place like that, you are on your own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You have to live by instinct, by some kind of a special whatever it is, because there's no one that can help you, other than yourself.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's what Auschwitz represented to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I became a survivor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I became a professional, the beginning of a professional survivor in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe, with all my heart, that young people survived, because they didn't know any better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe that, as a child, you are blessed, that you don't know any better.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing that hurts you is the yearning of your mother, the memories of that good, wonderful feeling of your family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only thing that hurt you is if you get beat and you feel the pain, and when you're hungry, because you have no other way of thinking ahead what's, what's happening to you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The intellect, the educated people, the culture, the aristocracy of Europe, of any nation, of [? urban, ?] they are the ones that could not survive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are the ones that went first, because they saw the predicament.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They saw what was going on, and said, what is there to live for?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've lost everything, my family, my children, my, my life, my profession.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what if I do get liberated, if ever, if there ever will be such a thing?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They let themselves go right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They saw the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As we say it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The, the, the, the true situation, the condition.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A child was-- did not have that ability.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So consequently, the children that survived, that were able to be, physically able to survive, did it only because we didn't know any better.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
